                            <comment id="14480156" author="paulk" created="Sat, 23 Feb 2013 05:33:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Proposed fix here:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/groovy/groovy-core/pull/142&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/groovy/groovy-core/pull/142&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
